{"tid":1166024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[神農氏] 中國據傳對美國進口藥品及醫療用品徵收25%關稅","createTime":"2019-05-22T07:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T08:07:57.000Z","uid":64191,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b1935bd38f1f3cafd1c288e3adcaafe3d41e5d6a","tid":1166024,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ashblowaway/status/1130308722432008192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fashblowaway%2Fstatus%2F1130308722432008192&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=f036e703\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fashblowaway%2Fstatus%2F1130308722432008192&h=3771f8f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ashblowaway/status/1130308722432008192</a><br />\n<br />\n其中收25%既包括胰島素、布洛芬、皮質類激素、前列腺素常用臨床藥物、B超診斷儀、超聲波設備、X光檢查造影、診斷試劑等等，合共2493種。<br />\n<br />\n而其他普通醫療用品都收5-10%不等關稅<br />\n<br />\n美國進口價增加，中國藥廠得以受益，銷售量將會大幅增加，特別係中國醫院開藥係同藥廠夾埋，廠要邊隻貨賣得好，醫院就跟住開呢隻藥，而唔係為病人度身訂造。<br />\n<br />\n中國百姓又可以重返神農氏嘗百草既年代，中國終成最大贏家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870bcdef82ba2fce07c37bc9a11867e9083ab5b8","tid":1166024,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"一車車來香港醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2677953a5adeccd82bbfa8792b5d2905ac4eece","tid":1166024,"uid":254259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80a7a06d6c3854043e50e14e6550a46c7af53ca6","tid":1166024,"uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"精彩放送<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AtvjugK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAtvjugK.jpg&h=196579bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9BtClZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https